      <title>波兰央行因能源价格推迟降息展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/polish-central-bank-delays-rate-cut-outlook-due-to-energy-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰央行表示，波兰政府决定只在明年 9 月之前降低能源价格，这导致通胀前景“复杂化”，并有效推迟了降息时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/polish-central-bank-delays-rate-cut-outlook-due-to-energy-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:05:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理支持的海上风电开发商 Corio 裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/macquarie-backed-offshore-wind-developer-corio-lays-off-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于可再生能源行业的各家公司都在努力削减成本，麦格理集团有限公司支持的海上风电开发商 Corio Generation Ltd. 正在裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/macquarie-backed-offshore-wind-developer-corio-lays-off-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希尔曼称特鲁多与特朗普的会晤非常顺利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/trudeau-had-great-meeting-with-trump-hillman-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大驻美国大使克尔斯滕·希尔曼 (Kirsten Hillman) 常驻华盛顿，她表示，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多上周五在特朗普的海湖庄园与当选总统唐纳德·特朗普进行了一次非常友好且富有建设性的会晤。希尔曼正在“平衡权力”。 (来源：彭博社)]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/trudeau-had-great-meeting-with-trump-hillman-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
